recipes.tip:
If you cant have eggs in your house buttermilk is a great substitute.Rice flour can be used in place of plain flour. Results will differ slightly. The coating is enough for three meals. Trust me, you want this coating in your pantry so stick to the full recipe and store the excess in an airtight container.
 
More variations are on my fb page and blog:www.facebook.com/theroadtolovingmythermomix
